data.title: Episode 2569 (14 August 2003)
data.meta_description: Janine prepares for the ultimate sacrifice to keep Barry. The Ferreiras' family wedding ends in chaos. Kareena Ferreira - Pooja Shah Tariq Laroussi - Nabil Elouahabi Dan Ferreira - Dalip Tahil Shirley Benson - Robyn Moore Adi Ferreira - Ameet Chana Ash Ferreira - Raji James Ronny Ferreira - Ray...
data.text:
The Ferreiras are getting ready for the wedding.

Janine realises she is going to have to sleep with Barry to make him forget about Natalie.

Dot takes being manageress of the laundrette a bit too seriously which annoys Pauline.

Sonia passes her exams and celebrates in the Vic. A dodgy plumber arrives to fix a broken toilet at the Vic.

Paul gets Barry a bit drunk in the Vic and they agree there is no going back for him and Natalie and that Barry should find comfort elsewhere.

Kelly finds out that Zoe has gone to the wedding and races over there with Tariq.

Martin shows Spencer his marijuana plants. Spencer is locked in the shed under the UV lights.

Shirley finds out that Dan's wife is alive.
